flowchart LR
  P[Photo of the monitor] --> D[Detect &amp; rectify the screen]
  D --> R[Locate each value field]
  R --> O[Read the digits OCR]
  O --> A[Assign to a parameter by colour/position]
  A --> V[Validate vs physiological ranges]
  V --> S[Structured vitals + confidence]
  V -. low confidence .-> H[Ask a human to confirm]
